snippet.title: "Kill the King" Multiplayer Playtest Announcement
snippet.description:
https://kill-the-king.com/playtest/

"Kill the King" is a cooperative, physics-based, VR sandbox. Become a deadly assassin and infiltrate massive castle environments to remove a corrupt king. Use your bow, swords, and anything else you find to reach your goal.
